flowchart TD
  Start([Start]) --> Initiate[Sales Department initiates Import Request]
  Initiate --> Input[Input Merchandise Code, Quantity, Unit, and Desired Delivery Date]
  Input --> Validate{Data is valid?}
  Validate -->|No| Error[Display Validation Error]
  Error --> Input
  Validate -->|Yes| Confirm[Confirm and Submit Request]
  Confirm --> Save[System generates Request ID and saves state as Submitted]
  Save --> End([End])
